636 VT_FALLBACK_SETTINGS = 14,
637 VT_ALLOW_NNAPI_CPU_ON_ANDROID_10_PLUS = 16,
638 VT_EXECUTION_PRIORITY = 18,
639 VT_ALLOW_DYNAMIC_DIMENSIONS = 20,
640 VT_ALLOW_FP16_PRECISION_FOR_FP32 = 22
641 };
642 const flatbuffers::String *accelerator_name() const {
643 return GetPointer<const flatbuffers::String *>(VT_ACCELERATOR_NAME);
644 }
645 const flatbuffers::String *cache_directory() const {
646 return GetPointer<const flatbuffers::String *>(VT_CACHE_DIRECTORY);
647 }
648 const flatbuffers::String *model_token() const {
649 return GetPointer<const flatbuffers::String *>(VT_MODEL_TOKEN);
650 }
651 tflite::NNAPIExecutionPreference execution_preference() const {
652 return static_cast<tflite::NNAPIExecutionPreference>(GetField<int32_t>(VT_EXECUTION_PREFERENCE, 0));
653 }
654 int32_t no_of_nnapi_instances_to_cache() const {
655 return GetField<int32_t>(VT_NO_OF_NNAPI_INSTANCES_TO_CACHE, 0);
656 }
657 const tflite::FallbackSettings *fallback_settings() const {
658 return GetPointer<const tflite::FallbackSettings *>(VT_FALLBACK_SETTINGS);
659 }
660 bool allow_nnapi_cpu_on_android_10_plus() const {
661 return GetField<uint8_t>(VT_ALLOW_NNAPI_CPU_ON_ANDROID_10_PLUS, 0) != 0;
662 }
663 tflite::NNAPIExecutionPriority execution_priority() const {
664 return static_cast<tflite::NNAPIExecutionPriority>(GetField<int32_t>(VT_EXECUTION_PRIORITY, 0));
665 }
666 bool allow_dynamic_dimensions() const {
667 return GetField<uint8_t>(VT_ALLOW_DYNAMIC_DIMENSIONS, 0) != 0;
668 }
669 bool allow_fp16_precision_for_fp32() const {
670 return GetField<uint8_t>(VT_ALLOW_FP16_PRECISION_FOR_FP32, 0) != 0;
671 }
672 bool Verify(flatbuffers::Verifier &verifier) const {
673 return VerifyTableStart(verifier) &&
674 VerifyOffset(verifier, VT_ACCELERATOR_NAME) &&
675 verifier.VerifyString(accelerator_name()) &&
676 VerifyOffset(verifier, VT_CACHE_DIRECTORY) &&
677 verifier.VerifyString(cache_directory()) &&
678 VerifyOffset(verifier, VT_MODEL_TOKEN) &&
679 verifier.VerifyString(model_token()) &&
680 VerifyField<int32_t>(verifier, VT_EXECUTION_PREFERENCE) &&
681 VerifyField<int32_t>(verifier, VT_NO_OF_NNAPI_INSTANCES_TO_CACHE) &&
682 VerifyOffset(verifier, VT_FALLBACK_SETTINGS) &&
683 verifier.VerifyTable(fallback_settings()) &&
684 VerifyField<uint8_t>(verifier, VT_ALLOW_NNAPI_CPU_ON_ANDROID_10_PLUS) &&
685 VerifyField<int32_t>(verifier, VT_EXECUTION_PRIORITY) &&
686 VerifyField<uint8_t>(verifier, VT_ALLOW_DYNAMIC_DIMENSIONS) &&
687 VerifyField<uint8_t>(verifier, VT_ALLOW_FP16_PRECISION_FOR_FP32) &&
688 verifier.EndTable();
689 }
690 NNAPISettingsT *UnPack(const flatbuffers::resolver_function_t *_resolver = nullptr) const;
691 void UnPackTo(NNAPISettingsT *_o, const flatbuffers::resolver_function_t *_resolver = nullptr) const;
692 static flatbuffers::Offset<NNAPISettings> Pack(flatbuffers::FlatBufferBuilder &_fbb, const NNAPISettingsT* _o, const flatbuffers::rehasher_function_t *_rehasher = nullptr);
693};

2083struct BenchmarkEventT : public flatbuffers::NativeTable {
2084 typedef BenchmarkEvent TableType;
2085 std::unique_ptr<tflite::TFLiteSettingsT> tflite_settings;
2086 tflite::BenchmarkEventType event_type;
2087 std::unique_ptr<tflite::BenchmarkResultT> result;
2088 std::unique_ptr<tflite::BenchmarkErrorT> error;
2089 int64_t boottime_us;
2090 int64_t wallclock_us;
2091 BenchmarkEventT()
2092 : event_type(tflite::BenchmarkEventType_UNDEFINED_BENCHMARK_EVENT_TYPE),
2093 boottime_us(0),
2094 wallclock_us(0) {
2095 }
2096};

2098struct BenchmarkEvent FLATBUFFERS_FINAL_CLASS : private flatbuffers::Table {
2099 typedef BenchmarkEventT NativeTableType;
2100 enum FlatBuffersVTableOffset FLATBUFFERS_VTABLE_UNDERLYING_TYPE {
2101 VT_TFLITE_SETTINGS = 4,
2102 VT_EVENT_TYPE = 6,
2103 VT_RESULT = 8,
2104 VT_ERROR = 10,
2105 VT_BOOTTIME_US = 12,
2106 VT_WALLCLOCK_US = 14
2107 };
2108 const tflite::TFLiteSettings *tflite_settings() const {
2109 return GetPointer<const tflite::TFLiteSettings *>(VT_TFLITE_SETTINGS);
2110 }
2111 tflite::BenchmarkEventType event_type() const {
2112 return static_cast<tflite::BenchmarkEventType>(GetField<int32_t>(VT_EVENT_TYPE, 0));
2113 }
2114 const tflite::BenchmarkResult *result() const {
2115 return GetPointer<const tflite::BenchmarkResult *>(VT_RESULT);
2116 }
2117 const tflite::BenchmarkError *error() const {
2118 return GetPointer<const tflite::BenchmarkError *>(VT_ERROR);
2119 }
2120 int64_t boottime_us() const {
2121 return GetField<int64_t>(VT_BOOTTIME_US, 0);
2122 }
2123 int64_t wallclock_us() const {
2124 return GetField<int64_t>(VT_WALLCLOCK_US, 0);
2125 }
2126 bool Verify(flatbuffers::Verifier &verifier) const {
2127 return VerifyTableStart(verifier) &&
2128 VerifyOffset(verifier, VT_TFLITE_SETTINGS) &&
2129 verifier.VerifyTable(tflite_settings()) &&
2130 VerifyField<int32_t>(verifier, VT_EVENT_TYPE) &&
2131 VerifyOffset(verifier, VT_RESULT) &&
2132 verifier.VerifyTable(result()) &&
2133 VerifyOffset(verifier, VT_ERROR) &&
2134 verifier.VerifyTable(error()) &&
2135 VerifyField<int64_t>(verifier, VT_BOOTTIME_US) &&
2136 VerifyField<int64_t>(verifier, VT_WALLCLOCK_US) &&
2137 verifier.EndTable();
2138 }
2139 BenchmarkEventT *UnPack(const flatbuffers::resolver_function_t *_resolver = nullptr) const;
2140 void UnPackTo(BenchmarkEventT *_o, const flatbuffers::resolver_function_t *_resolver = nullptr) const;
2141 static flatbuffers::Offset<BenchmarkEvent> Pack(flatbuffers::FlatBufferBuilder &_fbb, const BenchmarkEventT* _o, const flatbuffers::rehasher_function_t *_rehasher = nullptr);
2142};
